<item>
            <title>[LU-3040] Interop 2.2 server &lt;-&gt;2.4 client hang on test suite sanity 27p</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-3040</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;When testing 2.4 client against 2.2 server, sanity 27p hang looping in CLIO forever, because lli-&amp;gt;lli_layout_gen is different from cio-&amp;gt;cui_layout_gen. &lt;br/&gt;
See the attached log (sanity.27p) for details.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
        <key id="18112">LU-3040</key>
            <summary>Interop 2.2 server &lt;-&gt;2.4 client hang on test suite sanity 27p</summary>
