                                                                            <comments>
                            <comment id="220447" author="jay" created="Thu, 8 Feb 2018 18:15:38 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;close old tickets&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="54989" author="bergwolf" created="Thu, 28 Mar 2013 07:06:52 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Patch uploaded to &lt;a href=&quot;http://review.whamcloud.com/5866&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;http://review.whamcloud.com/5866&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;With the patch applied, client no longer hang.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="54894" author="bergwolf" created="Wed, 27 Mar 2013 06:29:03 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;I&apos;ve got two reports on this today, both running sanity test suits on 2.4 clients against 2.2 server. I have a small patch fixing it and our QA is helping verifying it. Once verified, I will upload it for review.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="54888" author="pjones" created="Wed, 27 Mar 2013 05:17:14 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Well, if that is the case then this would be a concern. How easy is it to hit this issue?&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="54887" author="bergwolf" created="Wed, 27 Mar 2013 04:17:51 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Peter,&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;I believe the issue exists for 2.1 server/2.4 client as well, if my bet on commit 9ac37e061 (&lt;a href=&quot;https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-2689&quot; title=&quot;Interop 2.1.4&amp;lt;-&amp;gt;2.4 failure on test suite runtests: Bad file descriptor&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;LU-2689&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;LU-2689&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; interop: use stripe md in ll_update_inode()) is correct.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="54886" author="bergwolf" created="Wed, 27 Mar 2013 04:15:56 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Commit 9ac37e061515(&lt;a href=&quot;https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-2689&quot; title=&quot;Interop 2.1.4&amp;lt;-&amp;gt;2.4 failure on test suite runtests: Bad file descriptor&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;LU-2689&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;LU-2689&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; interop: use stripe md in ll_update_inode()) looks suspicious. It may set lli-&amp;gt;lli_layout_gen to LL_LAYOUT_GEN_EMPTY even though server doesn&apos;t support layout lock.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="54885" author="pjones" created="Wed, 27 Mar 2013 04:13:50 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Peng Tao&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Interop with 2.2 is not supported for 2.4 - only 2.3 (adjacent release), 2.1(maintenance release) and 1.8 (widely used release)&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Peter&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
